§ Why ⦉
¶ ⦊
  ‖ If we have two manifolds, is there product a manifold? ⦉
⦉

§ Result ⦉
¶ ⦊
  ‖ The answer is yes. ⦉
⦉

<statement type='proposition'>
  ‖ Let $X$ and $Y$ be manifolds. Then $X ×Y$ is a manifold
    and $\dim X ×Y = \dim X + \dim Y$.
    † ⦊
      ‖ Future editions will include an account. ⦉
    ⦉⦉

